    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "OK, that's a fair point about a special case that won't include other special characters. Of course, there's no general way for LaTeX to have a macro escape that handles `$` or `\\`. If you'd like to simply close the issue, fair enough.\n\nIn any case, I'll encourage my students to use markdown cells pretty much all the time.\n"
